HEADWORD: Bregma
<hw>Breg"ma</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ the
front part of the head: cf. F. <ets>bregma</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>The point of junction of the coronal and
sagittal sutures of the skull.</def>⟦br⟧
